				Well, be thankful you got to be a part of these events.  The Fennin Ro server had like two events, one was in Gfay.  A GM named The Great Pumpkin was giving out small items, mostly wood and drink.  Another happened in.... surprise surprise Qeynos Hills.  Whilst these were ahppening I was off in the middle of both and could not get to either and was greatly dissappointed.  Not enough events happen on my server.  The events are typically in the same spot each time, they always either happen in the commons or in QH, both of which I have no interest in.  Am I supposed to just sit there all day and hope for an event?  I have better things to do.  I would love to see an event.  I also would love it if events where else were in the game.  Not everyone are always in these two places.  I personally wouldnt want to walk clear across Norrath jsut to see an event, because by the time I'd get there, I'dmissed everything.<BR>
